{"tid":2188158,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"隔牆有耳：獨家預言肥佬黎罪成 《星島》累藍絲空歡喜（李八方）","createTime":"2020-09-04T05:19:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-04T06:53:39.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"09ee73927b7092475ba736f090b9344fa0c1f363","tid":2188158,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T05:19:42.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200904/O52Q262KRBD6VE2DAOQSZCZBF4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200904%2FO52Q262KRBD6VE2DAOQSZCZBF4%2F&d=HMiOmB7b1AqxO%2BCwCPl1cU4axDeVXns42j9POfnWuxs%3D&h=e443e5ef\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200904%2FO52Q262KRBD6VE2DAOQSZCZBF4%2F&h=dc12cffc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200904/O52Q262KRBD6VE2DAOQSZCZBF4/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n隔牆有耳：獨家預言肥佬黎罪成<br />\n《星島》累藍絲空歡喜（李八方）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/xNFVFOUsCh48RoN29rTY16S8RYQ=/2554x2533/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/SGWBJMKXHFDUHDPQWCTZBFEZXA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FxNFVFOUsCh48RoN29rTY16S8RYQ%3D%2F2554x2533%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FSGWBJMKXHFDUHDPQWCTZBFEZXA.jpg&h=48d3d93c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n噚日係壹傳媒創辦人黎智英恐嚇《東方日報》記者案裁決日子，唔理黃定藍嘅市民必定睇實手機等裁決出爐，就係咁緊張時候，。。。。。<br />\n最神奇係，原來當時法庭仲未宣判！《星島》就先自行宣判肥佬黎罪成！<br />\n<br />\n話說《星島》網下晝2:35出呢單新聞，登出一分鐘之後，即刻有香討網民開post轉載報道，仲轉貼連結，旋即引嚟大批藍絲網民熱烈討論，有人支持「即時監禁」，但開心唔夠一陣，有人發現段文被鏟走，到下午3點左右各大傳媒都報道罪名不成立，搞到成班藍絲冇晒癮。樓主話想改標題但改唔到，只有沿用「黎智英涉刑恐記者 裁定罪成」呢個討論標題。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n老總：我都唔知喎<br />\n<br />\n今次《星島》搞到成班藍絲炒車，傷害佢哋嘅心靈，八方一於致電《星島日報》行政總裁兼總編輯黎廷瑤，問問點解有篇咁嘅報道，點知黎廷瑤話第一次得知呢件事：「咦，係咩，係咩？我都唔知喎！我再去了解一下先。」到底呢篇裁定罪成嘅文章點樣出現、消息從何而來呢？都係等《星島》慢慢研究。<br />\n<br />\n李八方"},{"pid":"d18d3698f7b58cde7aaba6adcadb15d0bf6932ff","tid":2188158,"uid":45733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T06:52:32.000Z","msg":"告佢誹謗"},{"pid":"aa463e358176ab366adf6e2be1ec584bdf05ff99","tid":2188158,"uid":302471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T06:53:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}